item.title: Need help with a new server!
item.dc:creator: @ersertaz ersertaz
item.description:
@ersertaz wrote:

the way u make peeps admin or mod or owner is to change their rights then compile

Rights Rank
0-regular player
1-player mod
2-admin
3-owner

if u want to test it make an acc then go to your characters folder. Click the testers acc name
then look for playerrights-0 then change the 0 to 3 then save it then click the compile.bat then try to log into it then say somein and u should see a gold crown and cg! ur owner or admin or pmod
